This app does not collect, store, or share any personal data.
It simply displays a hosted version of the open-source game OpenTTD (GPLv2) using a WebView.

The app does not use analytics, tracking, or third-party login services.
Network access is limited to loading the hosted game site at https://swords02.github.io/openttd-ios-web
 and the official OpenTTD content servers.

For information about the OpenTTD project, visit https://www.openttd.org
OpenTTD Privacy Policy: https://www.openttd.org/policy
